description: Gold Royalty Corp., a precious metals-focused royalty company, provides financing solutions to the metals and mining industry. It focuses on acquiring royalties, streams, and similar interests at varying stages of the mine life cycle to build a portfolio offering near, medium, and longer-term attractive returns for its investors. The company's portfolio consists of net smelter return royalties ranging from 0.5% to 2.0% on 17 gold properties located in the Americas. Gold Royalty Corp. was incorporated in 2020 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. David A. Garofalo B.Com., B.Comm, C.A., C.P.A., ICD.D
